#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "1520"
msgid "Quit  "
msgstr "Salir"

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "1527"
msgid "Cancel the order.  "
msgstr "Cancelar pedido."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "1547"
msgid "Order"
msgstr "Pagar"

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "1553"
msgid "Order the currently selected item.  "
msgstr "Pedir el artículo seleccionado."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "1590"
msgid "(I haven't picked anything.)  "
msgstr "(No he escogido nada)"

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "1621"
msgid "(I'm short on cash.)  "
msgstr "(Me hace falta dinero)"

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "1644"
msgid "Thank you. That'll be %s."
msgstr "Gracias. Eso sería %s."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "1670"
msgid "(I'd better not drink any more...)  "
msgstr "(Creo que ya es suficiente...)  "

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "1731"
msgid "A limited-edition whisky made to commemorate the 25th anniversary of the Yamazaki distillery."
msgstr "Un whisky de edición limitada hecho para conmemorar el 25º aniversario de la destilería Yamazaki."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "1825"
msgid "This is a whisky released by Yamazaki in 1984. It was created to commemorate the twenty fifth anniversary of the Yamazaki brand. "
msgstr "Este whisky fue lanzado por Yamazaki en 1984. Fue creado para conmemorar el 25 aniversario de la marca Yamazaki. "

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "1955"
msgid "Distilled and placed in barrels for aging in 1984, it is created from only the finest single malts. A symbol of 25 years of the Yamazaki brand. "
msgstr "Destilado y encubado en 1984 para su añejamiento. Elaborado exclusivamente con maltas de la más alta calidad. Símbolo del 25.º aniversario de la marca Yamazaki."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "2100"
msgid "This whisky is a blend of selected single malts aged in Japanese Mizunara oak barrels that are unique to the Yamazaki brand. "
msgstr "Este whisky es una mezcla de maltas únicas, añejadas en barricas de roble japonés Mizunara. Distintivas de la marca Yamazaki."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "2226"
msgid "This imparts into the whisky its Asian flavor, known around the world as the epitome of Japanese whisky.  "
msgstr "Esto le da al whisky su sabor asiático, conocido mundialmente como el mejor ejemplo del whisky japonés.  "

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "2333"
msgid "A Yamazaki whisky made with carefully selected, mature malts for a flavorful, smooth finish."
msgstr "Whisky Yamazaki elaborado con maltas cuidadosamente seleccionadas y maduradas, ofrece un final suave y sabroso."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "2426"
msgid "This is one of Japan's top single malt whiskies. It's become such a status symbol that whisky aficionados the world over have heard of it. "
msgstr "Este es uno de los mejores whiskies de malta pura de Japón. Un símbolo de estatus reconocido por aficionados de todo el mundo."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "2566"
msgid "They use carefully selected, perfectly matured single malts to get that great, smooth flavor. It's popular overseas, too. "
msgstr "Utilizan maltas cuidadosamente seleccionadas y perfectamente maduradas para conseguir ese sabor tan suave. También es popular en todo el mundo. "

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "2689"
msgid "A whisky made in the Southern Alps of Japan. Has a fruity flavor with smoky accents."
msgstr "Un whisky elaborado en los Alpes del Sur de Japón. Tiene un sabor afrutado con acentos ahumados."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "2774"
msgid "This one's made at Suntory's Hakushu distillery in Japan's South Alps, an area famous for its mountain spring water."
msgstr "Este whisky proviene de la destilería Hakushu de Suntory, en los Alpes del Sur de Japón; una región famosa por su agua de manantial."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "2891"
msgid "Its fruity, creamy flavor combined with a distinctly smoky accent makes for a superb drinking experience. "
msgstr "Su sabor cremoso y afrutado combinado con un acento claramente ahumado lo convierte en una experiencia de bebida excelente. "

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "2998"
msgid "I recommend taking the first drink straight up, to fully appreciate its quality."
msgstr "Recomiendo tomar el primer trago directamente, para apreciar completamente su calidad."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "3079"
msgid "A 30-year-old whisky with rich sherry notes and profound sweetness."
msgstr "Un whisky de 30 años con ricas notas de jerez y profundo dulzor."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "3147"
msgid "By the way, The Macallan has a brand new product called Fine Oak, which is a blend of single malts aged in bourbon and sherry barrels."
msgstr "Por cierto, lo nuevo de The Macallan es el Fine Oak, una mezcla de maltas envejecida en barricas de bourbon y jerez."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "3282"
msgid "But this one here was aged entirely in sherry barrels, using the traditional Macallan production method."
msgstr "Pero este de aquí fue añejado totalmente en barricas de jerez, siguiendo el método de producción tradicional de Macallan."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "3387"
msgid "The 30 year aging process produces a rich sherry note and a deep sweetness like ripe fruit. There's none of the wood taste of overaging."
msgstr "El añejamiento de 30 años da notas de jerez y un dulzor frutal profundo, evitando el gusto a madera por exceso de maduración."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "3524"
msgid "This one's incredibly smooth and it has a freshness you wouldn't expect from a 30-year-old whisky. It may be pricey, but one sip and you'll know that it's well worth it."
msgstr "Este es increíblemente suave y tiene una frescura que no esperarías de un whisky de 30 años. Puede ser caro, pero con un solo sorbo sabrás que vale cada centavo."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "3694"
msgid "A cheaper, yet still tasty, alternative to some of the pricier Macallan whiskies."
msgstr "Una alternativa más económica, pero igual de sabrosa, que los whiskies Macallan más caros."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "3776"
msgid "That's the standard of The Macallan line, aged entirely in sherry barrels. It's perfect for people who want to enjoy The Macallan without breaking the bank. "
msgstr "Es el estándar de la línea de The Macallan, añejado completamente en barricas de jerez. Es perfecto para quienes quieren disfrutar de The Macallan sin gastar una fortuna. "

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "3934"
msgid "It may be the standard bearer of the line, but it's guaranteed to deliver that classic Macallan taste. I recommend you experience its sweet, full flavor and aroma for yourself."
msgstr "Puede que sea el referente de la línea, pero te garantiza ese sabor clásico de Macallan. Te recomiendo probar por ti mismo su aroma y su dulce e intenso sabor."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "4111"
msgid "Characterized by an intensely smoky flavor and a smooth, dry body."
msgstr "Caracterizado por un sabor intensamente ahumado y un cuerpo suave y seco."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "4178"
msgid "It's safe to say this 10 year Laphroaig is the standard-bearer of the brand. It's characterized by an intensely smoky flavor and a smooth, dry body. "
msgstr "Es seguro decir que este Laphroaig de 10 años es el estandarte de la marca. Se caracteriza por un sabor intensamente ahumado y un cuerpo suave y seco. "

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "4328"
msgid "And it has more than its share of quirks, so most people either love it or hate it. If you end up loving this one, it'll be one drink you'll never forget."
msgstr "Su particularidad no deja indiferente a nadie, si llegas a apreciarlo, será una bebida que no olvidarás."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "4483"
msgid "A 12-year-old Scotch whisky with ripe, floral overtones."
msgstr "Un whisky escocés de 12 años con matices maduros y florales."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "4540"
msgid "That's the standard of the Bowmore line. Sherry barrels give it its uniquely ripe, floral overtones. Seaweeds unique to Islay give it a distinctive flavor and saltiness."
msgstr "Ese es el estándar de la línea Bowmore. Las barricas de jerez le dan matices florales y maduros únicos. Las algas marinas de Islay le aportan un sabor y salinidad distintivos."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "4710"
msgid "These qualities have caused it to be known as the Queen of Islay. It stands a cut above the rest of the single malt 12-year-old whiskies."
msgstr "Estas cualidades le han valido el título de Reina de Islay. Destaca con claridad sobre los demás whiskies de malta de 12 años."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "4848"
msgid "A unique bottle of whisky. Truly the peak of the Glenfiddich line."
msgstr "Una botella de whisky única. Ciertamente es la cúspide de la línea Glenfiddich."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "4915"
msgid "The 30-year-old stands at the pinnacle of the Glenfiddich line. It retains the brand's fruity sweetness, while adding a fullness only time can bring. "
msgstr "El Glenfiddich de 30 años se sitúa en la cúspide de la línea. Mantiene la dulzura afrutada de la marca, pero le suma un cuerpo que solo se logra con los años."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "5066"
msgid "It's a truly special bottle of whisky. It has a limited production each year, so it fetches a handsome price on the market. "
msgstr "Es una botella de whisky bastante especial. Tiene una producción anual limitada, así que alcanza un buen precio en el mercado. "

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "5191"
msgid "It's expensive, but you'll never regret drinking it."
msgstr "Es caro, pero no te arrepentirás de haberlo bebido."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "5244"
msgid "The best-selling single malt whisky in the world, known for its light and fresh flavor."
msgstr "El whisky de malta puro más vendido del mundo, conocido por su sabor ligero y fresco."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "5332"
msgid "Glenfiddich 12 Years is the best-selling single malt whisky in the world. This bottle set the industry standard for a single malt."
msgstr "Glenfiddch 12 años es el whisky de malta más vendido del mundo. Esta botella marcó el estándar de la industria de la pura malta."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "5463"
msgid "You'll find it light and fresh. The nose is full of fruit, and it has a clean finish, making it exceptionally easy to drink."
msgstr "Verás que es ligero y fresco. En nariz resaltan las notas frutales y tiene un final limpio, lo que lo hace excepcionalmente fácil de beber."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "5588"
msgid "Its light flavor makes it popular with the ladies and anyone new to single malt whiskies."
msgstr "Su ligero sabor lo hace popular entre las mujeres y cualquiera que sea nuevo en el mundo de los whiskies de malta."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "5678"
msgid "A rare Japanese whisky with a robust body."
msgstr "Un raro whisky japonés con un cuerpo robusto."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "5721"
msgid "One of the top premium whiskies in Japan and the whole world. A blend of single malts featuring whiskies aged for 32 years in a Yamazaki white oak barrel gives its distinct character."
msgstr "Uno de los mejores whiskies premium de Japón y del mundo. Una mezcla de malta única que presenta whiskies añejos durante 32 años en barricas de roble blanco de Yamazaki, lo que le otorga su carácter distintivo."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "5905"
msgid "Its quality has earned it a grand prize in an international competition. Only about 2,000 bottles are produced each year, making it especially rare."
msgstr "Su calidad le ha valido un gran premio en un concurso internacional. Sólo se producen unas 2.000 botellas cada año, lo que lo hace especialmente raro."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "6054"
msgid "If you really like whisky, this is one bottle you have to experience."
msgstr "Si realmente te gusta el whisky, esta es una botella que tienes que experimentar."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "6124"
msgid "One of Japan's premium brands, known internationally for its mellow flavor."
msgstr "Una de las marcas prémium de Japón, conocida internacionalmente por su sabor suave."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "6200"
msgid "This is a premium Japanese whisky that has won over whisky lovers around the world."
msgstr "Se trata de un whisky japonés premium que ha conquistado a los amantes del whisky de todo el mundo."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "6284"
msgid "This whisky starts with a single malt aged in Japanese Mizunara oak and then blended with over thirty different, painstakingly selected single malts."
msgstr "Este whisky inicia con una malta pura envejecida en roble Mizunara de Japón, para luego combinarse con más de treinta maltas puras, seleccionadas con sumo cuidado."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "6434"
msgid "The mellow flavor produced by this process has earned it a gold prize in an international competition. The finish is particularly good."
msgstr "El sabor suave producido por este proceso le ha valido una medalla de oro en una competencia internacional. El acabado es especialmente bueno."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "6570"
msgid "The best scotch available, hands down."
msgstr "Sin lugar a dudas, este es el mejor whisky escocés."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "6609"
msgid "This bottle is the pinnacle of Scotch whisky, head and shoulders above the competition."
msgstr "Esta botella es el pináculo del whisky escocés, muy por encima de la competencia."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "6697"
msgid "More than thirty different single malts aged over thirty years are hand-selected for their mellow character and blended. Truly the king of blended whisky."
msgstr "Para su creación, se seleccionan más de treinta maltas puras con tres décadas de añejamiento. Es sin duda, el rey de los whiskies mezclados."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "6852"
msgid "You can enjoy the taste of this whisky that can only be achieved by thirty years of aging. The fact that only 2,500 cases are bottled each year makes it quite rare."
msgstr "Puedes disfrutar del sabor de este whisky que solo se consigue tras treinta años de añejamiento. El hecho de que solo se embotellen 2,500 cajas cada año lo hace bastante raro."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "7017"
msgid "The crown jewel of the Ballantine's brand, crafted from a combination of over forty single malts."
msgstr "La joya de la corona de la marca Ballantine's, elaborada a partir de una combinación de más de cuarenta maltas."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "7115"
msgid "This is the ultimate blended whisky. It boasts a rich and smooth taste only made possible by combining over forty single malts."
msgstr "Este es el máximo exponente de los whiskies mezclados. Posee un sabor rico y suave que solo se logra combinando más de cuarenta maltas puras."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "7243"
msgid "This could very well be called the crown jewel of Ballantine's whisky blending skills. It's well-loved the world over, to the point of some calling it the best scotch ever made."
msgstr "Bien podría decirse que esta es la joya de la corona de la maestría de Ballantine's. Es tan apreciado en todo el mundo que algunos lo consideran el mejor escocés jamás creado."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "7421"
msgid "Standard Ballantine's scotch. Not too heavy, not too light, but just right."
msgstr "Whisky Ballantine's escocés clásico. Ni muy fuerte, ni muy suave, lo justo."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "7497"
msgid "That's a standard scotch, made from a blend of over forty varieties of single malts. Not too heavy, not too light. It's got a great balance to it."
msgstr "Ese es un scotch estándar, hecho a partir de una mezcla de más de cuarenta variedades de malta pura. Maneja un equilibrio perfecto."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "7644"
msgid "And the price isn't too high, either. I recommend it to casual scotch drinkers. It's also a nice intro to blended whisky, if you've never tried one before. "
msgstr "Además, el precio no es muy elevado. Se lo recomiendo a quienes disfrutan del escocés ocasionalmente. Es una buena forma de iniciarse en los whiskies mezclados si es tu primera vez."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "7801"
msgid "The biggest brand in American whiskey with a simple, clear flavor."
msgstr "Una marca de whisky americano de gran renombre, con un sabor sencillo y claro."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "7868"
msgid "When you think of American whiskey, this is it. A mellow, smooth taste is its defining feature."
msgstr "Cuando piensas en el whisky americano, este es el que viene a la mente. Un sabor sedoso es su característica definitoria."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "7964"
msgid "Made in the state of Tennessee, its unique charcoal filtering process officially qualifies it as Tennessee whiskey."
msgstr "New. Su exclusivo proceso de filtrado con carbón vegetal realizado en Tennessee, es lo que le otorga su identidad como whisky americano."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "8080"
msgid "However, it seems many people end up calling it a bourbon anyway."
msgstr "Sin embargo, parece que mucha gente termina llamándolo bourbon de todos modos."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "8146"
msgid "A silky bourbon with a sharp, clean finish."
msgstr "Un sedoso whisky bourbon, con un acabado nítido y limpio."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "8190"
msgid "People have enjoyed this bourbon since the day it first came out in 1860. It's the quintessential bourbon. The flavor is very American."
msgstr "Este bourbon ha cautivado al público desde su lanzamiento en 1860. Es precisamente ese sabor tan americano lo que lo convierte en la esencia misma de su clase."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "8326"
msgid "Silky and smooth on the tongue with a clean finish. This whiskey's reasonable price also makes it a wonderful choice for a casual drink."
msgstr "Sedoso y suave en la lengua, con un final agradable. El precio razonable de este whisky lo hace una elección genial para beber de forma casual."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "8463"
msgid "One of Japan's top brandies, famous for its fruity aroma and smooth flavor."
msgstr "Uno de los mejores aguardientes de Japón, famoso por su aroma afrutado y sabor suave."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "8539"
msgid "One of Japan's premium brandies, this bestseller has won over countless people with its bright, fruity bouquet and smooth taste."
msgstr "Es uno de los brandis más exclusivos de Japón. Este éxito de ventas ha conquistado a todos gracias a su aroma vibrante y frutal, junto con un sabor sedoso."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "8668"
msgid "V.S.O.P stands for Very Superior Old Pale, but you probably already knew that. "
msgstr "V.S.O.P son las siglas de Very Superior Old Pale, pero probablemente ya lo sabías. "

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "8748"
msgid "A remarkable specimen made by pairing the finest grapes with Borderies spirits."
msgstr "Un ejemplar extraordinario, elaborado a partir de las mejores uvas y destilados de Borderies."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "8828"
msgid "A remarkable specimen from France and the winner of a top prize in an international cognac competition."
msgstr "Un ejemplar extraordinario de Francia, ganador del gran premio en un certamen internacional de cognac."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "8932"
msgid "A blend of grapes from the four finest crus in the Cognac region produces a full but smooth palate. You haven't tasted cognac until you've tried this one."
msgstr "Una mezcla de uvas de los cuatro mejores crus de la región que ofrece un paladar rotundo pero suave. No sabrás lo que es el cognac hasta que lo pruebes."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "9087"
msgid "A premium Japanese beer made with only the finest malts."
msgstr "Una cerveza japonesa de primera calidad elaborada únicamente con las mejores maltas."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "9144"
msgid "This beer won Japan's first gold award in an international competition, and then defended the title for the next two years. It's a premium beer by Japanese and world standards."
msgstr "Esta cerveza obtuvo el primer oro internacional para Japón y mantuvo el título los dos años posteriores. Se trata de una bebida de alta gama según los estándares japoneses y globales."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "9321"
msgid "Unyielding commitment to quality ingredients and Suntory's years of brewing know-how produce a delicious, almost magical flavor. "
msgstr "Un compromiso inquebrantable con la calidad y los años de experiencia de Suntory dan lugar a un sabor delicioso, casi mágico."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "9451"
msgid "A frosty glass of this beer while nibbling sashimi or enjoying a Blu-ray movie on your day off... Now that's what I call living."
msgstr "Una copa bien fría de esta cerveza, mientras picas algo de sashimi o disfrutas de una película en tu día libre... Eso es lo que yo llamo vida."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "9580"
msgid "One of the most popular gins in the world, giving you that smooth juniper flavor with every sip."
msgstr "Una de las ginebras más populares del mundo, que ofrece ese suave sabor a enebro en cada trago."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "9677"
msgid "That's the gin drinker's gin enjoyed in 170 countries the world over. It's popular straight up or in cocktails like the martini. "
msgstr "Es la ginebra preferida de los puristas, presente en 170 países. Es ideal tanto para tomarla sola como en un martini."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "9807"
msgid "I'd bet any bar you walk into has at least one bottle of this gin. It's got a full juniper flavor, with a fresh citrus bite to it. I love to drink it as a gin and tonic. "
msgstr "Apostaría que en cualquier bar al que entres hay al menos una botella de este gin, tiene un sabor a enebro pleno, con un toque cítrico fresco. Me encanta beberlo como gin tonic. "

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "9978"
msgid "A balanced medium-grade golden rum."
msgstr "Un ron dorado de gama media y bien equilibrado."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "10014"
msgid "A nicely balanced, medium-grade golden rum. Lemon Hart is a well-known Demerara style rum produced in Guyana, located in the northern part of South America."
msgstr "Un ron dorado de gama media y bien equilibrado. Lemon Hart es un referente del estilo Demerara, producido en Guyana, al norte de Sudamérica."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "10171"
msgid "It's fermented and distilled along the banks of the Demerara River, then aged and blended in England."
msgstr "Fermentado y destilado a orillas del río Demerara, para después ser envejecido y mezclado en Inglaterra."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "10273"
msgid "This rum has a bright, yet deep aroma and a flavor that's powerful and elegant. Its faint, refined sweetness is a definite crowd pleaser."
msgstr "Este ron tiene un aroma brillante pero profundo y un sabor que es poderoso y elegante. Su sutil y refinada dulzura es un verdadero placer para el paladar."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "10411"
msgid "A smooth tequila made with nothing but the finest blue agave."
msgstr "Un tequila suave elaborado únicamente con el mejor agave azul."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "10473"
msgid "This brand is synonymous with premium tequila. This tequila uses one hundred percent blue agave, naturally fermented to create its all-natural taste."
msgstr "Esta marca define lo que es un tequila premium. Gracias al uso de agave azul puro y a una fermentación natural, ofrece un sabor totalmente genuino."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "10623"
msgid "It boasts excellent aroma and palate that enables you to fully appreciate tequila's allure. Either as shots or mixed in cocktails, you can't go wrong with it. "
msgstr "Presume de un aroma y un paladar excelentes que permiten apreciar todo el encanto del tequila. Ya sea en chupitos o combinada en cócteles, no tiene pérdida."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "10783"
msgid "An American vodka quickly rising in popularity due to its pure flavor and elegant design."
msgstr "Este vodka americano está en pleno auge por la pureza de su destilado y lo elegante de su presentación."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "10873"
msgid "That's an exceptionally well-known vodka. It's the fastest growing vodka brand in the U.S. these days. The elegant bottle design evokes the vast blue skies of California."
msgstr "Hablamos de un vodka excepcionalmente conocido, la marca de mayor crecimiento en EE. UU. actualmente. Su diseño recuerda a los vastos cielos de California."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "11044"
msgid "Their unique process of repeated distillation and filtration gives it a pure, smooth flavor. Maybe that's the secret behind its popularity. Either way, I recommend it."
msgstr "Su proceso único de destilación y filtrado repetido le otorga un sabor puro y suave. Quizás ese sea el secreto de su éxito; sea como sea, te la recomiendo."

